  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "ch39-01",
      "text": "C'est un saligaud !",
      "imagePrompt": "Medium shot, eye-level, of Avril facing the viewer as the mechanical spy-rat on the workbench projects a holographic image of Paul's angry face, Darwin hissing at the glowing projection. The spy-rat with its holographic beam is the focal point. Oil lamps and blue holographic glow light the underground lab, shocked and indignant mood.",
