      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "scoundrel",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-06",
      "text": "Le nom est là.",
      "imagePrompt": "Close-up, eye-level, of Avril leaning forward facing the viewer with wide eyes as Paul's holographic face speaks above the spy-rat on the desk. The glowing spy-rat projection is the focal point. Oil lamp light and the hologram's blue glow illuminate Avril's shocked face in the underground lab, revelatory and tense mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "the_name",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-07",
      "text": "C'est la faute du saligaud.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "the_name",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-08",
      "text": "Le nom du saligaud.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "the_name",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-09",
      "text": "La faute du saligaud a changé le monde.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "the_name",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-10",
      "text": "Paul dit le nom.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "the_name",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-11",
      "text": "Ça importe ici.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the underground laboratory, Avril sits facing the viewer clutching the mechanical spy-rat tightly against her chest, determination hardening on her face, brass equipment humming on the shelves behind her. The spy-rat pressed in Avril's grip is the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Warm oil lamp light catches her resolute expression, grave and determined mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "matters",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-12",
      "text": "On raconte l'histoire.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "matters",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-13",
      "text": "Ça importe à Avril.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "matters",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-14",
      "text": "L'histoire importe.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "matters",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-15",
      "text": "Ça importe parce que c'est la faute de la Ligue.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "matters",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-16",
      "text": "Ça chauffe ici.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the underground laboratory, Avril stands facing the viewer with clenched fists, steam rising from overheating brass equipment behind her, Darwin watching from a high shelf. The hissing steam vents on the agitated equipment are the focal point. Medium shot, eye-level. Oil lamps and steam-diffused light fill the room, heated and restless mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "heating_up",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-17",
      "text": "Il faut rester tranquille.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "heating_up",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-18",
      "text": "Ça chauffe dans le monde.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "heating_up",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch39-19",
      "text": "Avril n'est pas tranquille.",
